# OPENAI_API_KEY: Required for AI-powered features (Resume Builder, Cover Letter AI).
# This key enables GPT models for text generation and suggestions.
# 
# ⚠️ IMPORTANT SECURITY NOTES:
# 1. NEVER commit actual API keys to version control
# 2. Store keys securely in environment variables/secrets manager
# 3. Use different keys for dev/staging/production environments
# 4. If a key is exposed, regenerate it immediately in OpenAI dashboard
#
# 📍 UI BEHAVIOR:
# - If this key is missing or invalid, users will see an amber warning:
#   "API Configuration Required - AI features are disabled"
# - Non-AI features (PDF tools, image tools, calculators) continue working
# - Users are guided to contact administrator to enable AI features
#
# 🔑 HOW TO CONFIGURE:
# Local Development: Replace OPENAI_API_KEY value below with your actual key
# Vercel Deployment: Add OPENAI_API_KEY to Vercel Project Settings > Environment Variables
# Docker/Server: Inject via environment variable at runtime
#
OPENAI_API_KEY="sk-proj-xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx"

# APP_URL: The URL where this applet is hosted.
# AI Studio automatically injects this at runtime with the Cloud Run service URL.
# Used for self-referential links, OAuth callbacks, and API endpoints.
APP_URL="MY_APP_URL"

# VITE_GA_MEASUREMENT_ID: Google Analytics Measurement ID
# Used to track user visits and page analytics
# Get this from your Google Analytics property
VITE_GA_MEASUREMENT_ID="G-MY48Y5CKC6"
